'''James L. Cambias''' authored a number of RPG articles for the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]'', such as "[[You're in the Army Now!]] and "[[Wind Raiders of Taloraan]]." He was slated to write ''[[A Servant of the Empire]]'' for [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 16|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 16]] before it was canceled.

